snippet.textDisplay:
Fun fact: did you know CR7 has scored in more games for Juventus in his 1st 50 Serie A games than he did in his 1st 50 games in La Liga?

- scored in 31 games out of 50 Serie A games played, for a ratio of 62%
- scored in 29 games out of 50 La Liga games played, for a ratio of 58%

The difference? In La Liga, those 29 games scored in actually "produced" more goals:

- scored 40 goals in 50 Serie A games, for a goal ratio of 0.8
- scored 48 goals in 50 La Liga games, for a goal ratio of 0.96


This showcases how it's much easier to score in La Liga than it is in Serie A.

Turkish Falun Dafa practitioners gathered in front of the Chinese Consulate in Istanbul to protest and raise awareness about the persecution of the practice, which has been ongoing in China for the past 19 years. The activity took place during human rights week, on December 7, 2018.

Despite cold weather, the practitioners demonstrated the Falun Dafa exercises and held a press conference about the persecution in China.
